{"tid":1303213,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"施政報告諮詢 - 林鄭媽媽想對話呀！仲唔入去發表意見","createTime":"2019-07-10T08:33:51.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-10T09:02:27.000Z","uid":195614,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"904f7370cddb99711a08672b3b825b0937413666","tid":1303213,"uid":195614,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:33:51.000Z","msg":"《施政報告》諮詢工作展開<br />\n＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊＊<br />\n　　特區政府今日（七月十日）就二○一九年《施政報告》展開公眾諮詢。行政長官林鄭月娥、政務司司長張建宗和財政司司長陳茂波會陸續與不同界別人士會面，聽取他們的意見。<br />\n<br />\n　　林鄭月娥說：「要持續發展經濟，改善民生，需要我們一起籌謀，同心協力。我誠邀各位市民就《施政報告》發表意見，讓我們可以集思廣益，制訂切合市民需要的政策措施。我和我的團隊會虛心聆聽廣大市民的聲音，並在我的第三份《施政報告》中作出回應。」<br />\n<br />\n　市民可登入網站（<a href=\"http://www.policyaddress.gov.hk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.policyaddress.gov.hk&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=be913e20\" target=\"_blank\">www.policyaddress.gov.hk</a>）、在二○一九年《施政報告》公眾諮詢的Facebook專頁（<a href=\"http://www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FPolicyAddress2019&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=c3ed4bda\" target=\"_blank\">www.facebook.com/PolicyAddress2019</a>）或Instagram（<a href=\"http://www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Fpolicyaddress2019&d=q18Y%2F9yBacX5GGPSgvrSC5R%2B4kUINcy65scadR%2F1ewI%3D&h=a5793e04\" target=\"_blank\">www.instagram.com/policyaddress2019</a>）留言，亦可透過電郵（policyaddress@pico.gov.hk）、電話（2432 1899）或傳真（2537 9083）就《施政報告》提交意見。  <br />\n <br />\n完<br />\n2019年7月10日（星期三）<br />\n香港時間16時15分"},{"pid":"c6ebdc87816559bc9272624699da2f00612e298f","tid":1303213,"uid":161709,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T08:39:19.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>就嚟連票都冇得投喇</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: teal;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">緊急! 反DQ! <br />\n用自己email send 意見書!!! <br />\n生產器出嘅不受理</span></strong></span><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1302740\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1302740</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"c4721b6d6a18b5bfcec690b23bf5354ad375d27a","tid":1303213,"uid":186808,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-10T09:02:27.000Z","msg":"可唔可以喺自己本身意見以外，集中訴求，密集式俾一樣訴求？<br />\n<br />\nme:不要831框架，一人一票，重啟政改，普選行政長官"}]}